ground_truth:
First of all, for our benefit, we should draw in the desired angle: [asy]
pair pA, pB, pC, pD, pE;
pA = (0, 0);
pB = pA + dir(300);
pC = pA + dir(240);
pD = pC + dir(270);
pE = pB + dir(270);
draw(pA--pB--pC--pA);
draw(pB--pC--pD--pE--pB);
draw(pD--pA--pE, red);
